<strong>(Graywolf)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Donika Kelly sings this love to us in languages—rom her family&#8217;s Southern vernacular to the ecstatic compression of the sonnet‚that close the distance between grief and joy.”<br />
—Evie Shockley</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" data-attachment-id="260430" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/thomas-pynchon-marisa-meltzer-chris-kraus-and-more-24-new-books-out-today/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg.jpeg" data-orig-size="266,400" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Race Against Terror, Jake Tapper" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg-200x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg.jpeg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-260430" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg-200x300.jpeg" alt="Race Against Terror, Jake Tapper" width="200" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg-40x60.jpeg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg-33x50.jpeg 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/race-against-terror-9781668079447_lg.jpeg 266w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" /></p>
